  "root_text": {
    "iti16:0.1": "Itivuttaka 16 ",
    "iti16:0.2": "Ekakanipāta ",
    "iti16:0.3": "Dutiyavagga ",
    "iti16:0.4": "Paṭhamasekhasutta ",
    "iti16:1.1": "Vuttañhetaṁ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṁ: ",
    "iti16:2.1": "“Sekhassa, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno appattamānasassa anuttaraṁ yogakkhemaṁ patthayamānassa viharato ajjhattikaṁ aṅganti karitvā nāññaṁ ekaṅgampi samanupassāmi yaṁ evaṁ bahūpakāraṁ yathayidaṁ, bhikkhave, yoniso manasikāro. ",
    "iti16:2.2": "Yoniso, bhikkhave, bhikkhu manasi karonto akusalaṁ pajahati, kusalaṁ bhāvetī”ti. ",
    "iti16:2.3": "Etamatthaṁ bhagavā avoca. ",
    "iti16:2.4": "Tatthetaṁ iti vuccati: ",
    "iti16:3.1": "“Yonisomanasikāro, ",
    "iti16:3.2": "dhammo sekhassa bhikkhuno; ",
    "iti16:3.3": "Natthañño evaṁ bahukāro, ",
    "iti16:3.4": "uttamatthassa pattiyā; ",
    "iti16:3.5": "Yoniso padahaṁ bhikkhu, ",
    "iti16:3.6": "khayaṁ dukkhassa pāpuṇe”ti. ",
    "iti16:4.1": "Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. ",
    "iti16:4.2": "Chaṭṭhaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "iti16:0.1": "So It Was Said 16 ",
    "iti16:0.2": "The Book of the Ones ",
    "iti16:0.3": "Chapter Two ",
    "iti16:0.4": "A Trainee (1st) ",
    "iti16:1.1": "This was said by the Buddha, the Perfected One: that is what I heard. ",
    "iti16:2.1": "“Taking into account interior factors, mendicants, I do not see a single one that is so very helpful as rational application of mind for a trainee mendicant who hasn’t achieved their heart’s desire, but lives aspiring to the supreme sanctuary from the yoke. ",
    "iti16:2.2": "A mendicant rationally applying the mind gives up the unskillful and develops the skillful.” ",
    "iti16:2.3": "The Buddha spoke this matter. ",
    "iti16:2.4": "On this it is said: ",
    "iti16:3.1": "“There is nothing so helpful ",
    "iti16:3.2": "for a trainee mendicant ",
    "iti16:3.3": "aspiring for the ultimate goal ",
    "iti16:3.4": "as rational application of mind. ",
    "iti16:3.5": "Striving rationally, a mendicant ",
    "iti16:3.6": "attains the end of suffering.” ",
    "iti16:4.1": "This too is a matter that was spoken by the Blessed One: that is what I heard. "
  },
